577
00:28:15,560 --> 00:28:16,880
Did you get a good look?

578
00:28:17,840 --> 00:28:19,280
The place looks exquisite.

579
00:28:19,280 --> 00:28:20,360
Hao Weilai.

580
00:28:20,360 --> 00:28:21,880
What are you up to over there?

581
