649
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,320
The Milky Way?

650
00:31:11,360 --> 00:31:12,480
Wait, Siqi.

651
00:31:13,080 --> 00:31:13,920
If we're separated by The Milky Way,

652
00:31:13,920 --> 00:31:15,440
