743
00:39:42,360 --> 00:39:43,680
Attention!

744
00:39:43,680 --> 00:39:45,160
Left, face!

745
00:39:46,080 --> 00:39:47,720
Forward march!

746
00:39:57,160 --> 00:39:58,360
Scar.

747
00:39:59,360 --> 00:40:00,520
Quan.

748
00:40:04,120 --> 00:40:05,200
Mr. Xu.

