770
00:40:58,200 --> 00:40:59,280
Sure. Go ahead.

771
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:00,640
Go on.

772
00:41:01,200 --> 00:41:02,520
Just go.

773
00:41:09,200 --> 00:41:10,160
Wait. No.

774
00:41:10,920 --> 00:41:11,800
